pybricks-micropython (2.0.0~a3) stretch; urgency=medium

  * Improved sensor read performance
  * Added support for NXT sensors
  * Added support for generic I2C devices
  * Added support for generic UART devices
  * Improved motor control and synchronization
  * New Image class with improved screen drawing functionality
  * New Speaker class with improved sound functionality
  * New messaging module for Bluetooth communication
  * New EV3Brick class
  * Updated to MicroPython 1.11
  * Enabled MicroPython GIL for improved thread safety

